'''2-溴苯甲醚'''是一种[[有机溴化合物|有机溴化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>7</sub>H<sub>7</sub>BrO，属于溴代芳烃和芳香醚。

==合成==
由于苯甲醚的溴化反应的主产物是{{le|4-溴苯甲醚|4-Bromoanisole}}<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Catalysis Today|volume=194|issue=1|language=en|date=2012-10|pages=38–43|doi=10.1016/j.cattod.2012.05.012|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0920586112003604|title=In situ acidic carbon dioxide/water system for selective oxybromination of electron-rich aromatics catalyzed by copper bromide|accessdate=2020-11-27|author=An-Hua Liu, Ran Ma, Meng Zhang, Liang-Nian He|archive-date=2018-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180609233516/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0920586112003604|dead-url=no}}</ref>，一般选用其它方法制备2-溴苯甲醚，如[[2-溴苯酚|2-溴苯酚]]和[[硫酸二甲酯|硫酸二甲酯]]的甲基化反应。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Synthetic Communications|volume=37|issue=11|language=en|issn=0039-7911|date=2007-06-01|pages=1807–1815|doi=10.1080/00397910701316268|url=https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/full/10.1080/00397910701316268|title=Solvent‐Free Williamson Synthesis: An Efficient, Simple, and Convenient Method for Chemoselective Etherification of Phenols and Bisphenols|accessdate=2020-11-27|author=Ahmad R. Massah, Masumeh Mosharafian, Ahamad R. Momeni, Hamid Aliyan, H. Javaherian Naghash, Mohamad Adibnejad}}</ref>2-甲氧基苯硼酸和[[N-溴代丁二酰亚胺|NBS]]的反应<ref>{{cite journal|journal=RSC Advances|volume=7|issue=2|language=en|issn=2046-2069|date=2017|pages=764–770|doi=10.1039/C6RA25666J|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=C6RA25666J|title=A highly efficient heterogeneous copper-catalyzed chlorodeboronation of arylboronic acids leading to chlorinated arenes|accessdate=2020-11-27|author=Wen He, Rongli Zhang, Mingzhong Cai}}</ref>和2-甲氧基苯甲酸和[[四丁基三溴化铵|四丁基三溴化铵]]的反应<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Chemical Science|volume=9|issue=15|language=en|issn=2041-6520|date=2018|pages=3860–3865|doi=10.1039/C8SC01016A|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=C8SC01016A|title=Transition-metal-free decarboxylative bromination of aromatic carboxylic acids|accessdate=2020-11-27|author=Jacob M. Quibell, Gregory J. P. Perry, Diego M. Cannas, Igor Larrosa|pmid=29780518|pmc=PMC5935059}}</ref>也可以得到2-溴苯甲醚。

==反应==
2-溴苯甲醚和[[苯硼酸|苯硼酸]]在钯催化剂的存在下发生偶联反应，可以得到2-甲氧基联苯。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Organometallic Chemistry|volume=867|language=en|date=2018-07|pages=323–332|doi=10.1016/j.jorganchem.2018.01.033|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022328X18300391|title=PEPPSI-type complexes with small NHC ligands obtained according to the new method efficiently catalyzed Suzuki-Miyaura reaction|accessdate=2020-11-27|author=W. Sikorski, W. Zawartka, A.M. Trzeciak|archive-date=2022-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220303123627/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022328X18300391}}</ref>

